Finishing the Installation
These are the last bits to do before rebooting to your new system. It mostly consists of tidying up after the &d-i;.
&module-finish-install.xml;

  Miscellaneous



The components listed in this section are usually not involved in the
installation process, but are waiting in the background to help the
user in case something goes wrong.



